Lalina Gamer from Google

(May 15, 2018, 4:25 pm)

This school is great, i love the teachers... there soooo nice! and ive been there since kindergarden, so im like a citizen! i also love the food there, its better than what i could make at home! i also joined music makers, since i have quite a respect for music, and the pricipal was soo nice.... she greeted me everytime i got of the bus! tho i have to say that we need better bus drivers, i was half "deaf" and needed hearing aids but the bus always was too loud. and the bus needs to be on time so we can get to school on time! i also had a speech teacher, allbriton! she too is nice.
